{"tid":1218842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中］［輿論戰］[民意戰］大陸司法有問題嘅案件 list！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T23:31:27.000Z","uid":48516,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77353a3582c5848cb4f2d6c47db11a150ade7f22","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"聽到好多港豬都話唔犯法就無事，但好似有好多平民無端捲入官司，而又喺大陸得唔到公平嘅審訊。<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n谷開來案： 只有政府指定律師，審訊唔公開，案件詳細資料無公開<br />\n<br />\n豆腐渣工程：黃琦撰文揭發學校的豆腐渣工程，並協助死難者的父母提出申訴，其家人在6月14日接到通知「涉嫌非法持有國家機密」將其拘留。<br />\n<br />\n楊佳案：因騎一輛無牌照自行車，受到民警的詢問和盤查，後來獲釋。然而和許多同類情況一樣，楊遭毆打至生殖器損毁。楊多次上訪均未獲合理賠償，後來更不獲理睬<br />\n<br />\n瓮安事件：少女李樹芬於瓮安縣墜河身亡。李樹芬死亡原因有可疑之處，但當局不作立案，並強行要求將屍體埋葬，李樹芬家人作出阻止遭到毆打。<br />\n<br />\n新百倫：中國法院裁決一名註冊了「新百倫」商標的男子勝訴，New Balance即新百倫公司反而要賠償1,600萬美元。 （解釋到外資點解要走）<br />\n<br />\n孫小果案： 從死刑減到有期徒刑12年，再變身夜場老闆，「假立功真減刑」逃脱專項檢查<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲打可以補充，整完個list 出嚟後可以 share 俾啲人睇，整傳單&amp;poster，令啲師奶阿伯都知道平民百姓唔搞政治都會受影響。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cusp.hk/?p=1030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcusp.hk%2F%3Fp%3D1030&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ea93a7c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cusp.hk/?p=1030</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/113949/new-balance%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%A1%88%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-3%E9%96%93new-boom%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E8%A6%81%E8%B3%A01170%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F113949%2Fnew-balance%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-3%25E9%2596%2593new-boom%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25B3%25A01170%25E8%2590%25AC&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5ff9a28e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/113949/new-balance%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%A1%88%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-3%E9%96%93new-boom%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E8%A6%81%E8%B3%A01170%E8%90%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B0%B7%E9%96%8B%E4%BE%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BE%2586&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=76ddfa9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B0%B7%E9%96%8B%E4%BE%86</a>"},{"pid":"1c7181bce29909a7d47a1daa8e37f204654d603b","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf46cc8b2bafd7bc29b98a7125200e0189fcd815","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a446c01d7c73a6884dd4317753858467ab9462a","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"daf1234bc17ca5c75eca915a2bc7dcaf65a44937","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"40e481c642f08273cd0507ae767e65af43984a73","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7bed41f0a049c145f8b9a762cfd9336ee14d036b","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"915b8dcfc08c51c8e4ccd248427a9c8d4c309a9d","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc8efa2f702e070bf7d2354064e5e0689b50fd96","tid":1218842,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"538ffb227288ed1fec473244e6c8c304d77cc42a","tid":1218842,"uid":48516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc8efa2f702e070bf7d2354064e5e0689b50fd96","tid":1218842,"uid":703